Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.39,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}始まりはZERO　終わりならZET
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.98,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}疼くその手を 空にかざせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:10.48,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}始まりはZERO　終わりならZET
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.90,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}伏せたその目を いざ見開け
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.66,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}点線みたいに張り付く雨が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:21.06,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}つないで！つないで！と　叫んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:24.56,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}君の上にも降りかかる雨が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:28.46,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}僕の部屋の窓に打ち付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:33.13,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dot dot dot dot 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.29,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dot dot dot dot 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.71,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dot dot dot dot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:42.79,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dots and lines
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:49.33,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闇を彷徨う　無垢なLonely One
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:55.84,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}何を戸惑う君こそ神に選ばれしOnly One
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:01:01.57,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いちばん辛い事を知っているアイツは泣いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:08.62,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いちばん悲しい事を知ってるアイツは泣いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:10.00,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.25,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}another part of me another part of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:18.29,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}解き放つか否かは　貴方の人生一歩踏み出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:23.98,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その点と点の延長線上に待つ桃源郷へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:28.55,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dot dot dot dot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.39,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}起點是ZERO 終點是ZET
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.98,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}把隱隱作痛的手遮向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:10.48,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}起點是ZERO 終點是ZET
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.90,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}把那雙緊閉的雙眼 來吧睜開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.66,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}貼在墻面上的雨滴像珍珠般以點串線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:21.06,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}它們叫囂著發出彙聚的呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:24.56,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}滴落在你頭上的驟雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:28.46,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也激烈敲擊在我房間的窗戶上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:33.13,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dot dot dot dot 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.29,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dot dot dot dot 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.71,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dot dot dot dot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:42.79,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}零點 and 縱線！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:49.33,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}徘徊在黑暗之中的 純潔無垢的Lonely One
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:55.84,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}還在猶豫什麼 你就是被神選中的Only One
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:01:01.57,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}最了解煎熬是何感受的他並沒有哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:08.62,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}最明白悲傷是何體會的他並沒有掉淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:10.00,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}沒人能知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.25,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你的另一面 我的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:18.29,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是否要解放界限 在你的人生漫道中跨出一步 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:23.98,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}無數零點組成的縱線末段 桃源鄉在等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:28.55,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dot dot dot dot

Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:14.51,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誕生日が来るとね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:21.97,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}選ぶ　あなたへのプレゼント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:29.23,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}五番街通り 足をとめたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:35.03,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この愛代えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:45.30,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Darling　時計を止めて　頭を止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:51.25,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心を止める　目も、耳もぜんぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:57.93,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Darling　あなたにもらった言葉のすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:04.05,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}刺の無い薔薇を抱きしめたように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:08.82,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}hugging' you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:17.10,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Darling　この世界でふたり出会った奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:23.02,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その跡をつけてばかりの私、
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:28.43,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}lovin' you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:14.51,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}每一次生日來臨的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:21.97,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}挑選 給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:29.23,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哪怕駐足於第五大道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:35.03,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也無法買到我對你的這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:45.30,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}親愛的 停下時鐘 停止思考
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:51.25,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}停止心跳 眼睛..耳朵..停止你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:57.93,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}親愛的 你給予我的每一句話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:04.05,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我都會當做無棘的玫瑰緊緊抱在懷裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:08.82,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}擁抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:17.10,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}親愛的 兩人在這個世界邂逅的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:23.02,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只能悄悄跟在你後面的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:28.43,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深愛著你

Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行麼..Z·E·T
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才能覺醒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個吧 你的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你指的是修嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他去看著女高中生們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修最喜歡殺戮和女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他說只要留著性命想怎麼幹都行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算為了小葉她們..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能在這裡..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:29.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,0)}人質
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你在猶豫些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種非活即死的狀況下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子還想著絕對不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是比死掉還要煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考變得遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋和身體都沉重得要命..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的生命沉重得要命..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的“保護”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長老爺子啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z·E·T因子並沒有顯著地變化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不使用覺醒補充劑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用也不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說不定現在沒有帶在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是在家裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 阿人會死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人在嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一種方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 可以拿到一組意想不到的數據呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 沒法變成Z·E·T呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說中了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可難說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要殺一個人質試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兄弟之間就算分隔兩地也能交談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給他下命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你就吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 妳這什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的分身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來親一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛睜開 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不看的話我就讓那位小姐看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們家造出來的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害吧 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是PLAYER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了吧 害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們家造出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些PLAYER！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修的樣子不太妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要把那孩子殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果情況危急的話 就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發信源已經查出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C地區 底層 第六區塊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼城..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟想在下殺手之前和她們玩一玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快的話應該還來得及吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果你不成為Z·E·T
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就誰都別想救！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z·E·T因子雖在上升但是進展緩慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果沒有因子他剛才根本沒法有那種動作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以小看阿人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Z·E·T因子進入了下一個階段了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我會用全力把他殺了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 小葉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人之類的 我曾以為是用謊言拼湊起來的東西..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是..喜歡上他了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換個心情也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？失手了麼大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次換我出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行..藥..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z·E·T因子 又陷入沉默了麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應有波動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種現象是頭一回出現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算傷口能痊愈 但是如此不穩定的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對阿人身體的負擔太重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍不到裏面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面沒有設置攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪..明明感覺到了PLAYER的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦 是Z·E·T
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:09:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 小葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 不要出大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有一個男人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳再堅持一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我 先救朋美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的人優先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我自己會..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我很髒的..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒能馬上趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著你了啊 Z·E·T
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉 再稍微忍耐一下..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！阿..人..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我料理完他就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我回來之前一定要堅持住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能殺人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了你盡興！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這種程度麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋美..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳 朋美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行..使不上力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 Z·E·T
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怪物是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我是正義

Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是高雅呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把小葉..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？小葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊呼叫急救直升機！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於失血過多需要趕快輸血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一名受傷男子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有怪物在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間等直升機來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用飛行機座送去跟直升機碰頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.85,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,660)}FlyingHangar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你們來遠程操控
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行機座能坐多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然基本上是給阿爾法斯一個人用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是再加上小葉一人的話應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷男子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這裡還有一位小葉的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近住著很多流浪漢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還有怪物在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受害范圍會不斷增大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 超載了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小葉朋友和受傷男子留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且正如你所說 附近可能還有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有什麼閃失 對天城公司是個巨大的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我是阿爾法斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我問你一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大海中有三人溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救生艇只能坐兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而去救人的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在廉價的虛榮心驅使下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們假設你載上四人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能所有人都能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是遇難的幾率也十分之高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再假設你為了確保載客量而忍痛丟下兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和另一個人99%能平安回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更明智的選擇是哪一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問答是..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹和不知名的女高中生三人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選哪一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要一味地困擾他！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連這麼簡單的選擇題都不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法當好阿爾法斯的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊 高雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 小葉會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全沒有變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總在形式上下那麼多功夫..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了想像你一樣救死扶傷而得到了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了戰鬥的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近還有其他怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這些怪物們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管這些 你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人等著我去保護！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 你們快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥的傷很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被誰弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是欺負流浪漢的那幫人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這次換我們來收拾他們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直被小哥保護著..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是報答他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報答？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家都清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小哥保護著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次換我們來保護小哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 趕緊逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥才是趕緊逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你這幅身體可不能動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪物啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 小哥留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 這幫小龍蝦..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍蝦的話拿來烤了吃最好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z·E·T
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜碎們會死絕了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長..這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人還是沒有現身！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人會覺醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在PLAYER的暴力面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩獵者的血液不可能繼續沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡被地獄侵蝕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個白色的傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？阿爾法斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 趁現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z·E·T 再稍微努力一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 又見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定認為肉體受到一頓摧殘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游走於生死之間就能覺醒成Z·E·T了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 第一次和第二次都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 你剛生下來的時候的事情..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經超越了肉體遭受損傷就能覺醒的階段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你進入了最終階段了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就為你證明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰谷政次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾波爾中也算是高層了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.63,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,660)}EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道暴走之輪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它的碎片混入陶瓷中 完成的就是這個樁子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和暴走之輪會產生共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會適應的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼..阿人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一襲紅裝的你..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到了呢

